		h2 A few projects
		section
			.blurb
				img(src="../images/flower_circ.png" width=200 height=200).circleImage/
				.text
					h3 flower
					p.
						Want to show someone that you care? Make them a 
						#[a(href="http://harrisonbachrach.com/flower") flower]. [#[a(href="http://paperjs.org/") Paper.js]]
			.blurb(class='reversed_blurb')
				img(src="../images/disef2.png" width=200 height=200).circleImage/
				.text
					h3 DISEF
					p.
						When a snake has two heads,	they've got to work together to survive .
						Play #[a(href="http://harrisonbachrach.com/DISEF.html") DISEF] alone or with a friend and attempt to
						synchronize hands and minds. [Unity3D, C#]
			.blurb
				img(src="../images/notes_circ.png" width=200 height=200).circleImage/
				.text
					h3 Math 121A Notes
					p.
						After taking "Mathematical Tools for Scientists &amp; Engineers," I
						decided to compile #[a(href="") a set of notes for the course]. The project has
						expanded into a condensed guide to Multivariable Calculus, Linear
