		h2 Previous experience
		section
			.blurb
				img(src="../images/freelance_circ.png" width=200 height=200).circleImage/
				.text
					h3 Freelance Designer &amp; Illustrator
					p.
						I've been designing logos, T-shirts, posters, and websites for as long
						as I can remember. Check out #[a(href="https://www.behance.net/HarryB") my complete portfolio].
			.blurb(class='reversed_blurb')
				img(src="../images/lanl_circ.png" width=200 height=200).circleImage/
				.text
					h3 Los Alamos National Lab
					p.
						I spent a summer simulating and analyzing exploding stars, also known
